   while ( dbfPedCliI )->( dbSeek( ( D():PedidosClientes( nView ) )->cSerPed + Str( ( D():PedidosClientes( nView ) )->nNumPed ) + ( D():PedidosClientes( nView )  )->cSufPed ) ) .and. !( dbfPedCliI )->( eof() )
